data.description: GREAT OPPORTUNITY TO LIVE IN THIS BEAUTIFUL HOUSE!  Located in the desirable Wyndham Lakes area. ASSUMABLE MORTGAGE AT 3%. Enjoy the sunsets from the backyard and the most gorgeous view! High ceilings make this home very special. 4 beds home /2.5. Baths / Fenced in / Lake view. Stainless steel Appliances 2 years old only. You can have access to the deck from the master bedroom and enjoy the sunsets and the lake view! Zebra blinds in all the windows, newer AC unit, 2019 water heater, Hurricane accordion shutters though all the glass door and windows, fenced in. A+ GRADED SCHOOLS, Publix, Walmart, Gym, Doctors, Costco etc. conveniently located them 5 mins away that makes this home the perfect location! Low HOA, pool community and kids play area!
